                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>A section dedicated to Sage Service Fabric is available on the\u00a0<b>Option management</b>\u00a0page. It consists of two blocks:\u00a0<b>Configuration</b>\u00a0and\u00a0<b>Tax ID validation</b>. You can activate or deactivate Sage Service Fabric options such as tax ID controls from this section.</p>",
