                        {
                            "key": "XT-29889",
                            "title": "Rules for stock managed items and for the item-site replenishment",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>You need to define a stock managed item as a purchased and/or a manufactured item. On the Item-site page, you can define replenishment rules based on the item type and the replenishment method.<br/>\u00a0</p>",
